Package: rRace
Title: Predict race (also gender) form first name/last name pairings
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthias", "Matthias", , "Matthias.Uckert@Outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: 
    Wrapper around the R packages (predictrace, wru) and the python package ethnicolr.
    Standarizes the API and implements "GuessDiff" as an algorithm to choose between models.
    A short use case can be found on my github repo (https://github.com/MatthiasUckert/rRace).
